# Egg Timer üç≥‚è±Ô∏è

A simple, cute, and aesthetic egg timer created for fun!  
Designed with soft-girl vibes and pastel UI to make time management *less boring and more delightful* ‚ú®

---

## Features
- Set your own timer (minutes/seconds)  
- Soft pastel aesthetic design  
- Cute animation on timer completion  
- Works perfectly for cooking, study sessions, or mini breaks  

---

## How to Use
1. Open the `index.html` (or your main file) in a browser.  
2. Set the timer duration.  
3. Press **Start** and wait for the cute animation when time is up!  

